data.sentence: Para tu amor lo tengo todo.
data.translation: For your love I have everything.

data.sentence: Desde mi sangre hasta la esencia de mi ser.
data.translation: From my blood to the essence of my being.

data.sentence: Y para tu amor, que es mi tesoro.
data.translation: And for your love, that is my treasure.

data.sentence: Tengo mi vida toda entera a tus pies.
data.translation: I have my whole life at your feet.

data.sentence: Un corazón que se muere por dar amor.
data.translation: A heart that dies to give love.

data.sentence: Y que no conoce el fin.
data.translation: And that does not know the end.

data.sentence: Un corazón que late por vos.
data.translation: A heart that beats for you.

data.sentence: Para tu amor no hay despedidas.
data.translation: For your love there are no farewells.

data.sentence: Para tu amor yo solo tengo eternidad.
data.translation: For your love I only have eternity.

data.sentence: Y para tu amor que me ilumina.
data.translation: And for your love that illuminates me.

data.sentence: Tengo una luna, un arcoíris y un clavel.
data.translation: I have a moon, a rainbow, and a carnation.

data.sentence: Un corazón que se muere por dar amor.
data.translation: A heart that dies for giving love.

data.sentence: Y que no conoce el fin.
data.translation: And that does not know the end.

data.sentence: Un corazón que late por vos.
data.translation: A heart that beats for you.
Because of that I love you.
So much that I don't know.
